  <description>
    <p>McBoyard is an adaptation of the famous series which saw the light of day on France 2 in the 1990s in Minecraft. Hence its name "MC Boyard". Produced by ObeProd, we invite you to live the Fort Boyard experience in game. As if you were there in irl, you will face this stone ship in the middle of the water.</p>
